channel.title: Problem with new server
channel.description: Hi, I was wondering if anyone can help me with a server online/offline problem. I was trying to register my server on the server status page but when I clicked "Submit" it told me my server was offline :mad:. And I had my Runserver file on and I port forwarded. My friend's were able to get on perfectly fine using silabs webclient. I just cant seem to get on my server using Moparscape. Can anybody help me?
